dismissalText.commentary: Rahmanullah Gurbaz c †Abishek Porel b Starc 26 (12b 5x4 1x6 18m) SR: 216.66

dismissalComment.html: Appeal for caught behind. Starc is convinced. Umpires confer, send it upstairs. Was this a bump ball or a call for fair catch? Third ump says bump ball. The attempted yorker at 140ks landed beside the the batter's front foot. It was angling in towards off, Gurbaz tried to jam it with a straightish bat. There was a small gap between bat and pad, and he did indeed get an edge as the toe of the bat dug into the ground. The ball hovered and went low to Porel's right. He took it cleanly. KKR's highest opening stand for the season so far ends

dismissalComment.html: It is a hat-trick but for KKR! Hold on, Starc reckons there's an outside edge and DC review. Porel meanwhile takes aim, shoots and hits the stumps at his end, Russell has to keep running back to the dugout

dismissalText.commentary: Rahmanullah Gurbaz c †Abishek Porel b Starc 26 (12b 5x4 1x6 18m) SR: 216.66

dismissalComment.html: Appeal for caught behind. Starc is convinced. Umpires confer, send it upstairs. Was this a bump ball or a call for fair catch? Third ump says bump ball. The attempted yorker at 140ks landed beside the the batter's front foot. It was angling in towards off, Gurbaz tried to jam it with a straightish bat. There was a small gap between bat and pad, and he did indeed get an edge as the toe of the bat dug into the ground. The ball hovered and went low to Porel's right. He took it cleanly. KKR's highest opening stand for the season so far ends

First time Rahul has been run out in the IPL since 2022
